Mongo Database Collections Information
=======================================
Note : Its a first draft and needs more clarity

Product Catalog
	1) Item Name
	2) Description
	3) Tags
	4) Price
	5) Quantity
		
User Profiles
	1) User ID
	2) Name 
	3) Password
	4) Shipping Address
	5) Contact Information
	
Orders
	1) Order Number
	2) Items  (Name , Qty , Price)
	3) Total Amount
	4) User ID
	5) Order Creation Data
